166
00:11:52,580 --> 00:11:53,940
Is it the Mo family that needs me?

167
00:11:54,340 --> 00:11:55,659
Or is it you that wants my help?

168
00:11:55,659 --> 00:11:57,500
It's the Mo family!

169
00:11:58,820 --> 00:11:59,619
Feng Yang.

170
00:12:00,340 --> 00:12:02,659
You are the only daughter of our Mo family.

171
00:12:03,140 --> 00:12:06,140
Your future is also the future of the Mo family.

172
00:12:06,500 --> 00:12:08,539
My future is at the frontier,

173
00:12:08,539 --> 00:12:10,539
on the battlefield, and on my steed.

174
00:12:11,780 --> 00:12:14,659
My future will not be part of your scheme.

175
00:12:22,780 --> 00:12:23,859
So you know everything.

176
00:12:25,179 --> 00:12:28,419
I couldn't believe what you've done.

177
00:12:29,140 --> 00:12:30,500
