182
00:12:47,219 --> 00:12:49,299
I put all my hope in you.

183
00:12:49,299 --> 00:12:51,059
I value your strength the most.

184
00:12:51,179 --> 00:12:52,380
Do not become the one

185
00:12:52,380 --> 00:12:54,219
who disappoints me the most.

186
00:12:55,619 --> 00:12:57,580
Do you not care

187
00:12:57,580 --> 00:12:59,419
about your children's happiness?

188
00:12:59,619 --> 00:13:02,099
Eldest Brother, Eighth Brother,

189
00:13:02,099 --> 00:13:03,299
and I share the same fate.

190
00:13:03,500 --> 00:13:05,380
Fourteenth has a kind heart,

191
00:13:05,780 --> 00:13:07,179
yet you think nothing of him.

192
00:13:07,419 --> 00:13:09,219
