198
00:13:18,900 --> 00:13:21,460
your mother's last wish for caring all the people?

199
00:13:21,739 --> 00:13:23,219
I have never forgotten it.

200
00:13:24,260 --> 00:13:25,539
I will never forget it.

201
00:13:30,619 --> 00:13:31,460
Father.

202
00:13:36,179 --> 00:13:37,099
Take care.

203
00:13:40,859 --> 00:13:41,539
You...

204
00:13:58,900 --> 00:14:00,419
