208
00:14:09,500 --> 00:14:10,260
I don't care.

209
00:14:11,020 --> 00:14:12,659
Are you upset that I made the decision

210
00:14:13,340 --> 00:14:14,979
to bring you into war again?

211
00:14:17,260 --> 00:14:19,260
I was already tired of this boring place.

212
00:14:20,179 --> 00:14:22,940
The frontier may be a harsh land,
but at least we'll be free there.

213
00:14:28,979 --> 00:14:29,900
