choose another man over you.

219
00:15:13,659 --> 00:15:14,580
Don't worry.

220
00:15:14,780 --> 00:15:16,739
I will keep Fourteenth Young Master safe.

221
00:15:17,619 --> 00:15:18,580
All right.

222
00:15:19,099 --> 00:15:21,260
Is this a confession or a farewell?

223
00:15:23,500 --> 00:15:26,179
Feng Yang, I know you're a fearsome warrior.

224
00:15:26,340 --> 00:15:27,500
But the blades can cut anyone.

225
00:15:27,619 --> 00:15:29,500
You must be careful while you're there.

226
00:15:29,739 --> 00:15:32,739
After all, you have someone to look after.

227
00:15:35,859 --> 00:15:37,419
Don't worry.

228
00:15:37,419 --> 00:15:39,380
I will never let my man live in fear.

229
00:15:41,020 --> 00:15:41,940
Look at yourself.

230
00:15:42,299 --> 00:15:43,979
You are acting tough again.

231
00:15:44,859 --> 00:15:46,940
