260
00:17:15,500 --> 00:17:17,339
Very well, we should go now.

261
00:17:18,300 --> 00:17:19,180
Take care.

262
00:17:19,219 --> 00:17:20,060
Take care.

263
00:17:20,859 --> 00:17:22,099
- Take care.
- Take care.

264
00:17:22,979 --> 00:17:23,819
Take care.

265
00:17:24,420 --> 00:17:27,339
Prince Consort, shouldn't you join them?

266
00:17:28,020 --> 00:17:29,579
General has been the closest
with you since childhood.

267
00:17:30,180 --> 00:17:31,140
After she's left,

268
00:17:31,619 --> 00:17:33,219
there is no telling if you would meet again.

269
00:17:34,739 --> 00:17:35,540
Never mind.

270
00:17:37,619 --> 00:17:38,699
In her heart,

271
00:17:39,619 --> 00:17:41,859
I'm still the Eldest Brother she respects.

272
00:17:42,099 --> 00:17:43,739
Isn't that good enough?

273
00:17:45,859 --> 00:17:48,020
