00:21:02,339 --> 00:21:03,459
As Prince Consort of Crown Princess

318
00:21:03,699 --> 00:21:05,219
and a junior of Your Highness,

319
00:21:05,540 --> 00:21:06,780
my concern for Your Majesty

320
00:21:06,979 --> 00:21:09,579
