321
00:21:10,339 --> 00:21:11,459
I hope Your Majesty understands.

322
00:21:17,020 --> 00:21:18,099
Is that all?

323
00:21:19,819 --> 00:21:22,219
I've made my stance
as Prince Consort of Crown Princess

324
00:21:22,219 --> 00:21:23,099
very clear.

325
00:21:23,500 --> 00:21:27,459
But I have yet to speak to you, Qu Xiang Tan,
as Lian Cheng.

326
00:21:32,579 --> 00:21:34,540
Xiang Tan. It's time to let go.

327
00:21:35,060 --> 00:21:36,699
I had told you when we first met

328
00:21:36,900 --> 00:21:38,859
that you could end my life after you recovered,

329
00:21:39,099 --> 00:21:40,739
so we are now even.

330
00:21:40,979 --> 00:21:42,260
It's time to realize that.

331
00:21:43,660 --> 00:21:44,780
You love me!

332
00:21:44,780 --> 00:21:45,859
Young Master Lian Cheng you knew is gone.

333
00:21:45,859 --> 00:21:47,060
Don't you remember that?

334
00:21:47,300 --> 00:21:48,819
Why must you let this pain haunt you even now?

335
00:21:56,660 --> 00:21:58,219
Qu Tan Er is the cause.

336
00:21:59,579 --> 00:22:00,900
Who exactly is she?

337
00:22:01,020 --> 00:22:02,260
She is the woman I love.

338
00:22:03,099 --> 00:22:05,819
I don't care who she is. I love her.

339
00:22:06,020 --> 00:22:07,339
I don't believe it!

340
00:22:07,939 --> 00:22:09,619
You only love her because she looks like me!

341
00:22:09,939 --> 00:22:11,939
You will see that truth!

342
00:22:13,060 --> 00:22:14,619
I've told you everything.

343
00:22:15,260 --> 00:22:16,660
If I let you down,

344
00:22:16,660 --> 00:22:17,859
you could seek revenge on me.

345
00:22:17,859 --> 00:22:19,180
But please don't harm others.

346
00:22:20,739 --> 00:22:22,219
I hope our former bond

347
00:22:22,859 --> 00:22:24,300
wouldn't be ruined by what we've become.

348
00:22:32,180 --> 00:22:34,459
Your Majesty must take care.

349
00:22:35,699 --> 00:22:36,900
You've been agitated too many times,

350
00:22:37,180 --> 00:22:38,420
if you don't restrain your emotions...

351
00:22:39,900 --> 00:22:41,979
