352
00:22:43,979 --> 00:22:45,420
My body

353
00:22:46,660 --> 00:22:48,339
is already falling apart.

354
00:22:50,660 --> 00:22:51,979
It's time to give it up.

355
00:22:54,500 --> 00:22:57,619
Your Majesty, are you sure about this?

356
00:23:00,380 --> 00:23:01,900
Whoever she is,

357
00:23:03,780 --> 00:23:05,099
you will always love her.

358
00:23:07,420 --> 00:23:08,099
Very well.

359
00:23:11,459 --> 00:23:13,180
So be it!

360
00:23:26,699 --> 00:23:29,219
Why has Her Majesty summoned me to the palace?

361
00:23:29,780 --> 00:23:32,300
Your Highness, I do not know.

362
00:23:45,579 --> 00:23:47,099
Greetings, Your Majesty.

363
00:23:49,979 --> 00:23:51,939
Come here. Sit down.

364
00:23:52,420 --> 00:23:53,300
Much obliged, Your Majesty.

365
00:23:59,540 --> 00:24:02,060
Last night, the moonlight brought me
the reminiscence of the past.

366
00:24:03,140 --> 00:24:05,060
It's been far too long

367
00:24:05,300 --> 00:24:06,979
since we had talked like this.

368
00:24:10,020 --> 00:24:10,859
Try it out.

369
00:24:11,020 --> 00:24:13,459
These are your favorite osmanthus
cakes from your childhood.

370
00:24:14,739 --> 00:24:15,660
Thanks, Your Majesty.

371
00:24:26,180 --> 00:24:27,699
It does remind me of my childhood.

372
00:24:27,979 --> 00:24:29,660
It's been too long since I last tried this.

373
00:24:30,859 --> 00:24:32,780
It was your favorite.

374
00:24:33,780 --> 00:24:35,979
But Tan Er hated it.

375
00:24:36,459 --> 00:24:39,260
But she always pretended to like it

376
00:24:39,579 --> 00:24:40,979
just to cheer me up.

377
00:24:42,579 --> 00:24:45,459
Indeed. My sister had been sensible
since her childhood.

378
00:24:49,459 --> 00:24:51,180
But somehow,

379
00:24:52,180 --> 00:24:56,739
she seemed to have taken
a liking to different things.

380
00:24:56,739 --> 00:24:59,020
<i>Even Her Majesty has noticed it.</i>

381
00:24:59,060 --> 00:25:00,819
<i>This is a perfect chance.</i>

382
00:25:01,060 --> 00:25:02,699
I thought it was strange too.

383
00:25:02,979 --> 00:25:05,420
Crown Princess has become
much carefree than she was.

384
00:25:05,619 --> 00:25:07,500
She had multiple attempts
to realize gender equality.

385
00:25:07,739 --> 00:25:10,420
She behaved as if she was a different person.

386
00:25:10,739 --> 00:25:12,380
Her handwriting is an even more bizarre story.

387
00:25:12,579 --> 00:25:13,540
Not to mention...

388
00:25:15,660 --> 00:25:17,380
I shouldn't disrespect Her Highness.

389
00:25:17,540 --> 00:25:18,900
I deserve punishment.

390
00:25:20,380 --> 00:25:22,739
Never mind. Carry on.

391
00:25:25,260 --> 00:25:27,780
I've heard rumors from servants
working in Her Highness's residence

392
00:25:27,979 --> 00:25:29,979
that Her Highness had been acting
like a different person.

393
00:25:30,380 --> 00:25:33,339
She couldn't remember anything from the past.

394
00:25:34,020 --> 00:25:35,339
Is that true?

395
00:25:36,219 --> 00:25:37,540
I would never lie to Your Majesty.

396
00:25:40,660 --> 00:25:43,660
This is certainly weird.

397
00:25:44,339 --> 00:25:46,180
It concerns the royal bloodline.

398
00:25:46,380 --> 00:25:49,859
We must never draw conclusions
without hard evidence.

399
00:25:53,020 --> 00:25:54,180
I appreciate your concerns.

400
00:25:55,060 --> 00:25:56,140
As you know,

401
00:25:56,540 --> 00:25:59,739
I have always been impartial in treating you two.

402
00:26:00,540 --> 00:26:02,020
But compared to Qu Tan Er,

403
00:26:02,459 --> 00:26:04,459
you and I have more things in common.

404
00:26:08,900 --> 00:26:12,180
As Eldest Princess, you have great duties.

405
00:26:17,900 --> 00:26:20,459
I will do anything within my capability
to aide Your Majesty

406
00:26:20,619 --> 00:26:22,859
and cleanse Dongyue of any evil.

407
00:26:24,459 --> 00:26:25,420
Dismiss.

408
00:26:26,020 --> 00:26:26,939
I take my leave now.

409
00:26:37,094 --> 00:26:39,718
<i>Memorial</i>

410
00:26:40,060 --> 00:26:43,459
Your Majesty, I doubt it
that Eldest Princess could get this done.

411
00:26:43,699 --> 00:26:45,739
She is proud and competitive since young.

412
00:26:46,739 --> 00:26:49,540
She is never tired of her
competition with Qu Tan Er.

413
00:26:50,459 --> 00:26:52,420
She will make the best of this opportunity.

414
00:26:57,260 --> 00:26:58,140
How long will it take?

415
00:26:59,500 --> 00:27:00,859
There was an anomaly with the Soul-guarding Bead.

416
00:27:01,579 --> 00:27:03,339
I have subdued with by force.

417
00:27:04,300 --> 00:27:05,540
But as precautions,

418
00:27:05,900 --> 00:27:08,060
I need two more days for my preparation.

419
00:27:14,060 --> 00:27:16,819
Tan, you should stop swinging it.

420
00:27:16,939 --> 00:27:18,380
We've only finished building it just now.

421
00:27:18,500 --> 00:27:20,300
I think it's not very stable.

422
00:27:20,420 --> 00:27:23,060
I could reinforce the structure a little.

423
00:27:23,619 --> 00:27:24,420
No.

424
00:27:25,099 --> 00:27:26,939
This is the swing of love.

425
00:27:27,180 --> 00:27:29,300
Only we can build it.

426
00:27:29,540 --> 00:27:30,739
Isn't that right, Cheng Cheng?

427
00:27:31,619 --> 00:27:35,140
I think I built this on my own.

428
00:27:37,300 --> 00:27:39,819
The Royal Officer requests for an audience.

429
00:27:58,739 --> 00:28:01,140
How may I assist you?

430
00:28:01,540 --> 00:28:04,180
Her Majesty summoned Your Highness
to the royal study for a discussion.

431
00:28:04,979 --> 00:28:05,819
What is it?

432
00:28:06,459 --> 00:28:07,500
I do not know, Your Highness.

433
00:28:12,819 --> 00:28:13,859
It's all right, Cheng Cheng.

434
00:28:14,180 --> 00:28:15,180
It's the first time

435
00:28:15,180 --> 00:28:16,459
we've seen this kind of behavior.

436
00:28:16,739 --> 00:28:18,500
After all, I am Crown Princess.

437
00:28:18,739 --> 00:28:19,660
Don't worry about it.

438
00:28:20,579 --> 00:28:21,420
Be cautious.

439
00:28:23,619 --> 00:28:26,500
Make sure to finish the swing before I come back.

440
00:28:40,905 --> 00:28:42,600
<i>Yong</i>
<i>*Forever</i>

441
00:28:51,579 --> 00:28:52,619
Your Majesty.

442
00:28:52,780 --> 00:28:54,819
I must confront the woman next to me

443
00:28:55,219 --> 00:28:56,819
for impersonating my sister Qu Tan Er,

444
00:28:56,819 --> 00:28:59,099
sullying the royal bloodline
and the treason against the throne.

445
00:28:59,300 --> 00:29:00,979
She attempted to usurp the title of Crown Princess

446
00:29:00,979 --> 00:29:02,540
to seize control over Dongyue.

447
00:29:02,819 --> 00:29:04,739
I fear that my real sister

448
00:29:05,020 --> 00:29:06,619
has met her demise.

449
00:29:07,099 --> 00:29:08,619
Please be our judge, Your Majesty.

450
00:29:08,619 --> 00:29:10,300
My sister deserved justice.

451
00:29:10,819 --> 00:29:11,699
Mei Er.

452
00:29:13,500 --> 00:29:17,060
Do you know what the punishment
for slander against Crown Princess is?

453
00:29:17,979 --> 00:29:20,739
Your Majesty, she is framing me.

454
00:29:22,939 --> 00:29:25,219
She is clearly jealous of my title,

455
00:29:25,459 --> 00:29:26,780
so she decided to tarnish my name.

456
00:29:27,140 --> 00:29:29,260
My sister used to have fair handwriting.

457
00:29:29,260 --> 00:29:30,979
But this woman has inferior handwriting.

458
00:29:31,020 --> 00:29:33,020
According to the servants
in Second Princess's Residence,

459
00:29:33,420 --> 00:29:36,219
my sister used to master all forms of art.

460
00:29:36,500 --> 00:29:38,060
This woman is nothing compared to her.

461
00:29:38,500 --> 00:29:40,579
This woman prefers spicy food

462
00:29:40,579 --> 00:29:42,579
and wears brilliant colors,
all while behaving abnormally.

463
00:29:42,939 --> 00:29:44,859
The differences between her
and my sister are apparent.

464
00:29:45,939 --> 00:29:48,140
I do not believe in her stories of amnesia.

465
00:29:48,140 --> 00:29:49,699
They are clearly two different people.

466
00:29:50,380 --> 00:29:51,939
I hope Your Majesty brings her to justice.

467
00:29:57,660 --> 00:29:58,939
What is your counterargument?

468
00:30:01,540 --> 00:30:04,699
Your Majesty, my handwriting changed

469
00:30:04,979 --> 00:30:08,180
because of the side-effect after I drowned.

470
00:30:08,380 --> 00:30:10,180
My hands became too weak.

471
00:30:10,900 --> 00:30:12,819
As for the statements from her eyewitnesses,

472
00:30:12,819 --> 00:30:14,619
she could have bought them off easily.

473
00:30:14,979 --> 00:30:17,619
Not to mention asking me to prove

474
00:30:17,819 --> 00:30:19,339
my own identity

475
00:30:19,339 --> 00:30:21,420
is illogical at best.

476
00:30:22,939 --> 00:30:24,180
Eldest Princess,

477
00:30:24,660 --> 00:30:27,459
how can you prove you're not an impostor?

478
00:30:30,300 --> 00:30:31,699
I have always acted the same way.

479
00:30:32,099 --> 00:30:33,900
Unlike you, you've changed so much.

480
00:30:36,780 --> 00:30:39,579
Your Majesty. After the accident,

481
00:30:39,859 --> 00:30:42,339
I had issues with my memories.

482
00:30:43,020 --> 00:30:44,500
After my close encounter with death,

483
00:30:44,780 --> 00:30:47,540
I decided to change my way of living.

484
00:30:48,500 --> 00:30:50,420
I didn't want anyone to pick on me.

485
00:30:59,739 --> 00:31:01,380
My changes in behavior

486
00:31:01,780 --> 00:31:03,579
were caused by the accident.

487
00:31:03,979 --> 00:31:06,060
If Your Majesty wishes to investigate,

488
00:31:06,579 --> 00:31:09,219
we could start by investigating
why I fell into the water.

489
00:31:10,099 --> 00:31:11,900
Do not shift the topic.

490
00:31:12,219 --> 00:31:14,500
There is no connection between
your identity and the accident.

491
00:31:19,020 --> 00:31:21,020
It could be you who murdered her

492
00:31:21,219 --> 00:31:22,660
and took her place.

493
00:31:24,780 --> 00:31:27,780
Your Majesty, my poor sister
deserved to have justice.

494
00:31:29,619 --> 00:31:31,300
I am Qu Tan Er!

495
00:31:31,500 --> 00:31:33,660
Nothing will change that fact.

496
00:31:35,540 --> 00:31:38,500
Your Majesty, look at my cute face,

497
00:31:38,780 --> 00:31:40,619
my slim figure,

498
00:31:40,859 --> 00:31:42,699
this is who I am!

499
00:31:48,020 --> 00:31:49,619
Mei Er's doubts

500
00:31:50,099 --> 00:31:51,900
raised some questions for me.

501
00:31:55,060 --> 00:31:58,540
But Tan Er's statements are logical.

502
00:32:02,060 --> 00:32:04,699
Princess's identity is a serious matter.

503
00:32:06,380 --> 00:32:07,099
Mei Er.

504
00:32:08,060 --> 00:32:10,939
I leave the investigation to you.

505
00:32:15,140 --> 00:32:17,780
Qu Tan Er shall be imprisoned for the time being.

506
00:32:18,260 --> 00:32:20,420
She may retain her title
as the heir apparent in East Palace.

507
00:32:20,900 --> 00:32:24,939
We shall take further action
after we've known the truth.

508
00:32:25,579 --> 00:32:26,300
Your Majesty.

509
00:32:27,260 --> 00:32:30,180
Wise judgment, Your Majesty.
I will carry out the order.

510
00:32:37,020 --> 00:32:37,979
Guards.

511
00:32:40,979 --> 00:32:42,459
Take Second Princess to the prison.

512
00:33:14,579 --> 00:33:15,420
Cheng Cheng!

513
00:33:18,339 --> 00:33:19,380
What happened?

514
00:33:21,060 --> 00:33:22,900
She is an impostor.

515
00:33:23,619 --> 00:33:25,339
She will wait for her hearing in prison.

516
00:33:25,500 --> 00:33:26,260
Wait.

517
00:33:26,619 --> 00:33:28,380
This must be a setup.

518
00:33:40,939 --> 00:33:42,780
Are you going to disobey Her Majesty's order?

519
00:33:45,180 --> 00:33:46,859
Cheng Cheng, don't worry.

520
00:33:48,380 --> 00:33:49,619
Whatever the case is,

521
00:33:49,979 --> 00:33:51,739
I still retain my title as Crown Princess.

522
00:33:51,900 --> 00:33:54,420
As my lesson to become the next Empress,

523
00:33:54,819 --> 00:33:57,020
I should experience the harshness of life.

524
00:33:58,020 --> 00:34:00,099
Don't worry. I won't be gone for long.

525
00:34:01,819 --> 00:34:03,819
Tan Er, wait for me.

526
00:34:06,820 --> 00:34:07,500
Let's go.

527
00:35:02,580 --> 00:35:03,659
Snobs.

528
00:35:35,580 --> 00:35:37,179
The watery rice isn't that bad.

529
00:35:38,219 --> 00:35:40,300
It would be great with some pickles

530
00:35:40,300 --> 00:35:41,300
and chili sauce.

531
00:35:48,580 --> 00:35:50,459
Her Majesty arrives!

532
00:36:49,260 --> 00:36:50,340
Greetings, Your Majesty.

533
00:36:52,699 --> 00:36:53,379
I can't believe

534
00:36:53,379 --> 00:36:55,540
you have the appetite to eat even at such a place.

535
00:36:56,540 --> 00:36:57,500
Your Majesty, I knew

536
00:36:57,739 --> 00:36:59,899
this was part of your plan.

537
00:37:00,139 --> 00:37:02,659
Your Majesty is wise,
so there must be a reason to this.

538
00:37:02,939 --> 00:37:05,540
The meal is decent.

539
00:37:05,820 --> 00:37:07,780
The cell provides shelter from the wind and rain.

